  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca77c7ee-ec6c-44be-9537-1bb3c3c98d55\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d0157ae-f844-469d-ae21-59683f7043f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3c739471-8e21-4bb9-bcfb-90060d8de6d7\"><b>안녕하세요 언제나 건강하게! 이수한의원 입니다.</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3bd8dee3-8590-4bc8-b6e8-398dbdb53b0e\"><b> </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ca77c7ee-ec6c-44be-9537-1bb3c3c98d55\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ac406d7-e3c0-40a1-9fc9-57dea9498eac\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"10\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_10.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a68b5294-ec0d-4af4-8a21-de0caeee1cc9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a0d29bea-92f3-4f46-b54d-42da5e44d1b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-3a03107f-f92c-408d-9f77-8101ebd314da\"><b>하체 붓기·체형 불균형, 원인은 ‘골반 틀어짐’?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a2ab918-4fb9-4a81-be79-c4fd87f00a36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82af40e1-2af3-4d00-b306-9a94f654514a\">하루 종일 서 있거나 앉아 있으면 다리가 쉽게 붓고, 시간이 지나면서 다리 라인이 무너지는 경험을 하신 적 있으신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-35e6d502-cd78-4631-b858-7f569b78c76c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-be55c1af-43bb-49cb-a1a7-48354f01682c\">단순히 하체 순환이 안 되는 문제일 수도 있지만, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e83eeb26-fb9e-4dd9-8b87-41a82a220d39\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b55457d4-4794-44f6-8be6-712b6b9f4b9a\"><b>골반의 틀어짐</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-adf6464d-33e2-45c7-bbe9-5f2129f2904c\">이 근본 원인일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aaae5481-ad3b-4165-b51e-ce326a9f6306\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2b789c9d-5483-44b2-bb0f-6ec98e14dc13\">골반은 우리 몸의 중심으로, 척추와 하체를 연결하는 중요한 역할을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f06a4519-0a35-4a66-af9c-509437dadeb4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-58abd27b-d25e-426f-a1cb-b0e7fb2d97d9\">조금만 틀어져도 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e62ae9ca-a336-42a0-9463-6698beac8dac\"><b>체형 불균형, 하체 비만, 순환 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6bda8363-1c0b-48cc-a063-a3a680fe717c\">까지 이어질 수 있기에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fefd8d26-4830-4c93-8591-d0a57b5d7efa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9b5b8b1f-0336-4f1b-a00a-88ae27eb100c\">조기 관리가 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a68b5294-ec0d-4af4-8a21-de0caeee1cc9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9bd2e3cf-55fd-4533-915d-26faf10dffa2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65cdf90e-9a3c-4bdf-9320-f00988d6b5c5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-65cdf90e-9a3c-4bdf-9320-f00988d6b5c5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c71aae584ba52a67.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1700\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c71aae584ba52a67.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c71aae584ba52a67.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-65cdf90e-9a3c-4bdf-9320-f00988d6b5c5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e9fbd159-85bd-4f30-8a44-80d2fa747210\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cc3b40cb-1a5d-4796-aac3-b3e1545f55db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4e98724-1917-4232-ae0a-7390109b2599\"><b>골반 틀어짐이 만드는 문제들</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4cf0a6d-0d9c-4de7-a48d-6b0ac38958e3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3ce38678-4f07-47b8-88ed-e57b78f9816d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38d0dc5e-5379-4535-99f2-969e1a1bf3ed\"><b>하체 비만</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-55d61a79-4a8f-4ea5-a214-5217fec317d6\">: 골반이 기울어지면 하체 근육과 지방 분포가 불균형해져 살이 잘 찝니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a2db4d6-4da5-404e-b402-1fc51cb8dfd5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ed39475-18d0-4dd6-9383-1ae53f6902be\"><b>다리 붓기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cf9954bc-6f27-4d57-aca7-32f1ee7a65ca\">: 혈액과 림프 순환이 원활하지 못해 부종이 반복됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ecf01f81-d6eb-4184-b99a-45e78ff193f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-79efa5b5-7aff-475d-87cd-99f7deba9fdf\"><b>휘는 다리(O·X다리)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5368017e-e451-447d-bec2-cf72f4a4b9df\">: 무릎 관절에 부하가 걸려 다리 모양이 변형됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b0b472e8-6f22-4766-9dbc-d19c1b6e17dc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-96a5391d-8601-4d51-83e6-aefcb032ede1\"><b>허리·골반 통증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-25582453-7c6a-4f03-a39b-87de7137e338\">: 근육 불균형으로 만성 통증이 생기기도 합니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-b4cf0a6d-0d9c-4de7-a48d-6b0ac38958e3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d660540d-780f-4220-8fa2-b2aad6db4a3c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-0d37c168-5289-450c-97e8-7313fea27ace\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cbd7bb66-cf76-45d3-9d87-f5e1f38c64c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f35f7156-66d4-4f48-8214-4c245af2237c\"><b>잘못된 습관이 골반에 미치는 영향</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7db50202-6e81-49ff-9b16-aa4900f275b2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eff0e386-5931-498e-a6ce-07371eccf70b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd37ea9d-6407-436a-8fdd-f3ca1b98aa3c\">다리를 꼬고 앉는 습관</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3529614e-51fd-4634-a71f-0f61a31ecdc0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-616782a1-8a3b-461b-bffa-134ce82a3190\">높은 하이힐을 자주 신는 생활</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23870ea5-b093-4808-a18a-69d034b7f68d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2e534988-c6d6-4249-bac2-92a808ab9412\">장시간 같은 자세로 앉아 있는 직업</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-335d5bc1-b750-49e3-a380-06d2504d45eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73007635-2309-4608-b5e4-2079b47658f3\">비뚤어진 자세로 걷는 습관</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef79d8df-4179-44c6-aa60-bd42bd153a5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c0774668-876d-492a-a793-2ad1b1e24150\">이런 작은 습관들이 쌓여 골반을 틀어지게 만들고, 결국 하체 건강까지 위협합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7db50202-6e81-49ff-9b16-aa4900f275b2\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'