d72ae2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6eae549e-87df-4065-afc7-67379dccfa25\"><b>바른 자세 앉기·서기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3af9290b-0ebc-409b-87c5-eb2f757efdf3\">: 엉덩이를 의자 깊숙이 붙이고 허리를 곧게 세우기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2fe2c2f7-3eb3-4a6d-8c2c-e694314193e8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d7694be4-12ac-49d2-b8b8-cefcdd4a8b8a\"><b>하체 스트레칭</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aaafc2e4-ecad-4f1f-820e-529ea2a7ae8b\">: 고관절·햄스트링 스트레칭으로 근육 균형 맞추기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7aa3fd77-d390-4060-9669-356d3fdc57b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7c7c4dea-de1d-4fe6-87c2-d2ae372959f8\"><b>가벼운 근력운동</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5904f769-a5c1-4159-954f-e8d9a56c8a38\">: 스쿼트·브릿지 운동으로 골반 안정화</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cecac5d8-c2a9-4972-9253-5884a4048ed6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-10d0d28e-f1e5-4697-bbe2-7cc10f34220d\"><b>편한 신발 착용</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b5648600-0a91-42a0-9d5b-eddfd3e6b42b\">: 하이힐 대신 발에 무리가 가지 않는 신발 선택</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-cb234856-d864-45a3-93c7-c047c56d6902\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-ae4f7a4a-1c26-4af9-9125-66456fdb901e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <